      <div class="help-row">
        <span class="help-icon">📖</span>
        <span class="help-text">For advanced pattern configuration visit the <a href="/admin/fields" style="color:#1677ff">Fields page</a> or see <a href="/admin/pattern-help" target="_blank" style="color:#1677ff">📖 Pattern Help</a>.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tips -->
    <div class="help-section" style="border-right:none">
      <div class="help-section-title">💡 Tips &amp; Tricks</div>
      <div class="help-row">
        <span class="help-icon">🌐</span>
        <span class="help-text">The page auto-detects <strong>Hebrew text</strong> and sets RTL. Override per-card with the direction button.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="help-row">
        <span class="help-icon">⚡</span>
        <span class="help-text">Upload <strong>3 files at once</strong> to compare redaction across different document types in parallel.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="help-row">
        <span class="help-icon">🕵</span>
        <span class="help-text">Use the <strong>search</strong> to verify a specific name or number was redacted — search in the Redacted pane to confirm the replacement, or in the OCR pane to see the original.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="help-row">
        <span class="help-icon">🎯</span>
